    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设新家园</h2>建设你的幸存者基地，供他们在冒险之余休息、闲聊。播种作物，驯服外星野兽，引入免于失落命运的科技成果，巩固你们的家园，抵御虎视眈眈的敌人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/9c58763d4b6a5ddf37b9ca118ee21c6d.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/9c58763d4b6a5ddf37b9ca118ee21c6d.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/9c58763d4b6a5ddf37b9ca118ee21c6d.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >置身复杂而且颇需战术考量的战场</h2>战场抢占上风将不会只是鼠标指指点点那么简单。命中模拟与生命系统将十分精细，即便是非致死的中弹都有可能令幸存者丧失作战能力。虽然火力压制能把敌人钉在原地，但是你的弹药一旦耗尽，下一场遭遇战就没法打了。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/80ecaebb9ff6a91622dfa2fde8005c3f.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/80ecaebb9ff6a91622dfa2fde8005c3f.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/80ecaebb9ff6a91622dfa2fde8005c3f.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驾驶修好的载具</h2>外面的世界很大，光靠11路可走不了多远，你需要更好的交通工具。《Ascent of Ashes》与同类游戏存在一个巨大的不同，那就是玩家能够修理、驾驶被人弃置的车辆和载具。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/325135811313ee84fa893cb33ce98798.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/325135811313ee84fa893cb33ce98798.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/325135811313ee84fa893cb33ce98798.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >领导你的幸存者</h2>幸存者各有各的性格，各有各的想法。你身为基地的领袖，需要征召有才有能的幸存者，壮大拓殖队伍，才能克服与日俱增的困难。你能让所有人都开心、满意、安心、积极吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/749f1024640e1237407e73e7150cd266.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/749f1024640e1237407e73e7150cd266.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/749f1024640e1237407e73e7150cd266.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索陌生的新世界</h2>整个程序生成的世界宽广辽阔，可以看到各种自然环境与特别地点。要想在末世之后的世界生存下去，就要走进“崩塌”发生之前的废墟，闯过其中的重重险关。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/23c8d60503125534de0715037a31e052.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=672 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/23c8d60503125534de0715037a31e052.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/23c8d60503125534de0715037a31e052.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI随机应变</h2>游戏不仅要有各种机制构成深入的作战系统，还要有敌人能够利用这些机制对付你才行。不同的敌人智能水平各不相同，强盗这种散兵游勇或许不难应付，但是训练有素的残军小队就完全是另一回事了。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/25c84f3398563e27763314d31fda837d.poster.avif?t=1753444799\" width=634 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/25c84f3398563e27763314d31fda837d.webm?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209140/extras/25c84f3398563e27763314d31fda837d.mp4?t=1753444799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《边缘世界》“Combat Extended” Mod创作团队出品</h2><strong>《边缘世界》“Combat Extended” Mod</strong>的创作团队开创了拓殖模拟这个游戏类型的先河，游戏设计重点围绕探索、平衡与策略展开，令经典末世之后生存游戏的深度模拟系统融合了经典即时战略与回合制杰作的战术元素。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持Mod</h2>我们团队诞生于Mod创作，我们多年来也有幸加入了众多优秀Mod制作社群，因此希望通过《Ascent of Ashes》回馈这些社群。游戏的引擎完全由我们自己开发，只为尽量消除拓展的困难，而且有赖于我们丰富的Mod制作经验，我们非常了解Mod创作这需要哪些支持。《Ascent of Ashes》是Mod佬为Mod佬开发的游戏。",
